{"type":null,"faqId":38995,"title":"刚睡醒时，翻腕亮屏等功能不可用是怎么回事？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.33333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:14pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p4{text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span>考虑到您的睡眠质量，手环贴心的进行了一些功能设置，比如暂停使用翻腕亮屏功能以免打扰您休息。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span>刚睡醒时，手环还没有退出睡眠模式，此时翻腕亮屏等功能不可用。您可以滑动屏幕3次以上，或者下床活动一下，然后翻腕亮屏功能就可以正常使用了。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4305","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":59,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}